\pard\f0\fs28   {\b A. pseudocotula} Boiss., {\i Diagn. Pl. Or. Nov.} {\b 1}({\b 6}): 86 (1846) has been doubtfully recorded from Karpathos. It is like {\b 39} but has the peduncles clavate in fruit and the outer achenes persistent and with an auricle up to ½ as long as the achene.
